---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="MetaboLab - エビデンス×データで考えるメタボ対策" description="40代〜50代男性のための、科学的エビデンスに基づくメタボ対策メディア。データで裏付けられた効果的な方法をお届けします。">
  <section class="hero section">
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <h1>データが示す、<br />正しいメタボ対策を。</h1>
      <p>最新の研究データとエビデンスに基づいた、<br />効果的なメタボ改善方法をお届けします。</p>
      <a href="/metabolab/categories/diet" class="btn btn-primary">記事を読む</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/metabolab-hero/800/500" alt="MetaboLab" loading="eager" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>カテゴリから探す</h2>
      <div class="category-grid">
        <a href="/metabolab/categories/diet" class="card category-card">
          <span class="category-icon">📋</span>
          <h3>ダイエット</h3>
          <p>エビデンスに基づくメタボ改善食事法</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/metabolab/categories/exercise" class="card category-card">
          <span class="category-icon">💪</span>
          <h3>運動</h3>
          <p>科学的に効果が実証された運動メニュー</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/metabolab/categories/sleep" class="card category-card">
          <span class="category-icon">📊</span>
          <h3>睡眠</h3>
          <p>睡眠データが示すメタボとの関係</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/metabolab/categories/recipe" class="card category-card">
          <span class="category-icon">🍽️</span>
          <h3>レシピ</h3>
          <p>栄養バランスの取れた実践的レシピ</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/metabolab/categories/mental" class="card category-card">
          <span class="category-icon">🧠</span>
          <h3>メンタル</h3>
          <p>ストレス管理とメタボの関係性</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-tint">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>最新の記事</h2>
      <div class="article-list">
        <article class="card article-card">
          <img src="https://picsum.photos/seed/metabolab1/400/250" alt="記事イメージ" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="article-card-body">
            <span class="tag">ダイエット</span>
            <h3>メタボ改善に効く！科学的に正しい糖質制限とは</h3>
            <p class="article-date">2025-06-18</p>
            <a href="/metabolab/posts/low-carb-evidence" class="btn btn-outline">続きを読む</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  .hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a252f 0%, var(--color-primary) 100%);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .hero-content { flex: 1; }
  .hero-content h1 { color: #fff; font-size: var(--font-size-3xl); }
  .hero-content p { color: var(--color-bg); }
  .hero-image { flex: 1; }
  .hero-image img { border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg); width: 100%; }

  .category-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }
  .category-card {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-text);
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }
  .category-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .category-icon { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); }
  .category-card h3 { font-size: var(--font-size-lg); margin-top: 0; }
  .category-card p { font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--color-text-light); }

  .bg-tint { background: #eef0f2; }

  .article-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-lg); }
  .article-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .article-card img {
    width: 280px;
    min-height: 180px;
    object-fit: cover;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .article-card-body { flex: 1; }
  .article-date { font-size: var(--font-size-sm); color: var(--color-text-light); }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero { flex-direction: column; }
    .article-card { flex-direction: column; }
    .article-card img { width: 100%; }
    .category-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
